{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\">As the new Pyrotechnician, you are the keeper of dreams in a peaceful village, Natsuwa. Your mission? Infuse every moment with wonder! \ud83d\ude0d</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2989660/extras/header.png?t=1739093475\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Harness the power of your creative fireworks designed by yourself to transform the village's life into unforgettable memories in this slow and melancholic narrative-driven drawing game, Firework Syndrome. \u2728\ud83e\udd79</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Whether it's marking birthdays, nurturing friendships, or listening to stories from the villagers, your enchanting touch will leave an indelible mark on this wonderful community. Choose carefully the fireworks you want to use, the village may have to make decisions that could change the lives of its inhabitants and you could be part of it.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2989660/extras/capture.png?t=1739093475\" /></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Craft unique fireworks to celebrate special moments and etch them into the hearts of the villagers.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Weave bonds of camaraderie among the villagers by crafting touching memories.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Discover stories of the inhabitants, revealing the village's secrets as you go.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Witness your artistry come to life in a stunning display that illuminates the night sky and warms every heart in the village.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p>","background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2989660/page_bg_generated_v6b.jpg?t=1739093475"